        <!-- primary outcomes -->
    <div class="body3">Primary Outcome Measures:
      <ul style="margin-top:1ex; margin-bottom:1ex;">
            <li style="margin-top:0.7ex;">Efficacy outcome was change in score on the Conners Abbreviated Symptom Questionnaire for Teachers (ASQ-T) [&nbsp;Time&nbsp;Frame:&nbsp;at 16 weeks&nbsp;] [&nbsp;Designated&nbsp;as&nbsp;safety&nbsp;issue:&nbsp;No&nbsp;]<br/>
            </ul>
    </div>
    <br/>
    
        <!-- secondary outcomes -->
    <div class="body3">Secondary Outcome Measures:
      <ul style="margin-top:1ex; margin-bottom:1ex;">
            <li style="margin-top:0.7ex;">the ASQ-Parent (ASQ-P) and Child Global Assessment Scales (C-GAS). Adverse events were monitored using AE logs, the Pittsburgh Side Effects Rating Scale, vital signs and electrocardiograms [&nbsp;Time&nbsp;Frame:&nbsp;at 16 weeks&nbsp;] [&nbsp;Designated&nbsp;as&nbsp;safety&nbsp;issue:&nbsp;No&nbsp;]<br/>
            </ul>
    </div>
